A Nigerian footballer, Jude Ighalo Yesterday, celebrated his wife’s birthday by getting her a brand new Range Rover. He wrote, ‘Happy birthday to my beautiful wife.may your life be filled with love and happiness.I LOVE YOU’. His happy wofe, Sonia also shared photos of her new whip saying, ‘Time and again you ve made me realized that i am a Super lucky wife..Thanks alot for gifting me such an incredible present’. The post Super Eagles striker,Jude Ighalo gifts his wife a brand new Range Rover on her birthday.